Package herencia

Class Course

  • java.lang.Object
    • herencia.Course
  • public class Course
extends java.lang.Object
    The Course class represents an educational course with various attributes such as identifier, name, capacity, modality, schedule, classroom, instructor (professor), and price. This class provides constructors, getter and setter methods for each property, and a toString method for easy representation of a Course object.
